"""
ANALYSIS FRAMEWORK:
1. Decade-wise analysis (1985-1994, 1995-2004, 2005-2014, 2015-2024)
2. Region-wise aggregations using averages (not sums where inappropriate)
3. Trend analysis for climate patterns
4. Meaningful insights for agricultural and environmental planning

KEY ANALYSIS AREAS:
‚Ä¢ Temperature Trends: Average T2M changes, Max/Min shifts, Regional variations
‚Ä¢ Rainfall Patterns: Average PRECTOTCORR, Seasonal variations, Regional distribution
‚Ä¢ Other Parameters: Humidity, Solar radiation, Wind speed, Soil moisture trends

CALCULATION NOTES:
‚Ä¢ Rainfall: Using average mm/day, not sum
‚Ä¢ Temperature: Average values
‚Ä¢ Regional analysis: Weighted averages by district
‚Ä¢ Trend analysis: Decade-wise comparisons
"""
